{"tid":682643,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利記球迷死亡恐嚇　卡利奧斯妻兒無一幸免","createTime":"2018-05-29T04:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T06:44:51.000Z","uid":122,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7ce7b0d5b6c160fd1e08fe2b4e6859b4e68fd45d","tid":682643,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T04:38:14.000Z","msg":"利物浦在歐聯決賽遭遇滑鐵盧，門將卡利奧斯(Loris Karius)兩次失誤成為眾矢之的，賽後連番表示悔意都難阻球迷的謾罵，更有球迷留言恐嚇表示會殺害卡利奧斯的親人。事後默西賽德警方已經接手調查相閞事件，雖然卡利奧斯有感謝球迷支持，讓他有如置身大家庭當中，不過看來並非所有球迷都是他的「家人」。<br />\n<br />\n卡利奧斯雖然在賽後連番在社交網站出文向利物浦球迷致歉，但依然有球迷不領情，同樣在社交網站作出言語恐嚇以及咒罵，指會殺害他的女兒，詛咒他的兒子及家人。默西賽德警方向外國媒體Telegraph透露會調查事件，在社交的言論非常激進和具攻擊性，會調查事件是否具威脅。<br />\n<br />\n引用Posts from Liverpool fans included a comment saying, &quot;I&rsquo;ll murder your girl I&rsquo;ll murder your girl&quot;.<br />\n<br />\nOthers said his &ldquo;sons deserve to die of cancer&rdquo; and &ldquo;I hope your whole family dies&rdquo;.<br />\n<br />\n卡利奧斯再次有災難性演出讓利物浦的門將位置亮起紅燈，本以為他在賽季後半段表現好轉能讓球會專注補強其他位置，可惜事與願違，相信球會上下給予卡利奧斯的機會已經足夠多，與其留在球隊被千夫所指不如租借離隊「過冷河」，對球員來說或許是較佳選擇。"},{"pid":"2fc5d206e7fe6024ec58b230d27c72eb17305607","tid":682643,"uid":14374,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T04:42:00.000Z","msg":"猁迷入黎討論"},{"pid":"8c76a6f338200dec369390e81f837519f254d26c","tid":682643,"uid":143582,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T04:43:03.000Z","msg":"YNWA!"},{"pid":"cf0b9addd1db2018f7025835988241b72448e6b7","tid":682643,"uid":179283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T04:45:12.000Z","msg":"猁迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a08f37c4bea29c475e7d6e71d387416f0f724d4","tid":682643,"uid":1977,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T04:45:36.000Z","msg":"You will never walk again<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f36a8d9d4adf479d9a8688af1d45828cb0d1a9b","tid":682643,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T04:46:58.000Z","msg":"死猁狗縮返晒入去自己老母個狗閪度？"},{"pid":"efde425862b5d323d5972b20fd5db521be216ee3","tid":682643,"uid":283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T04:47:28.000Z","msg":"賭仔黎<br />\n利迷唔會咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5c4a820d24f281db903a6a71318f4b550ba18f","tid":682643,"uid":140233,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:02:49.000Z","msg":"佢未結婚同埋冇仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1f0e7ce96fee08dcb3bcff737ce70fea28a0e7","tid":682643,"uid":137006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:09:56.000Z","msg":"You better not walk home alone"},{"pid":"1e6c5064c01de75bdfbe242158a7722732ffcedf","tid":682643,"uid":174013,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:10:07.000Z","msg":"你又知係利迷？<br />\n唔比係曼迷扮？"},{"pid":"f2021a0b958be2350623b49613ac3466e0b2da2a","tid":682643,"uid":119157,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:13:40.000Z","msg":"講句屌你老母 就真係要放條野係你老母度咩<br />\n<br />\n小學雞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"668676961885570d9c2aeb9858b19aea2fe842d4","tid":682643,"uid":50656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e6c5064c01de75bdfbe242158a7722732ffcedf","tid":682643,"uid":174013,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:10:07.000Z","msg":"你又知係利迷？<br />\n唔比係曼迷扮？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:15:06.000Z","msg":"係曼迷嘅話就寫篇感謝狀比佢啦"},{"pid":"8be666bb7e5a9d35d8a97e8fb641a3c178abe4a7","tid":682643,"uid":87394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:15: